Description: Those who enter the Widow training program are given crash courses in Teamwork, Tactical Analysis and Coordination of Assets.

Powers.DescLong: You are more evasive to melee attacks.
A good leader knows how to protect his team. While active, this power increases the Defense of yourself and all nearby teammates to all attacks.

Powers.DescShort: Toggle: Self Res (Psionics, Disorient, Hold, Immobilize, Sleep, Fear, Confuse, Repel, Knockback).
Powers.DescLong: When you toggle on this power, it grants protection from Sleep, Disorient, Fear, Immobilize, Confusions, Repel, Knockback and Hold effects. Indomitable Will also grants moderate resistance to Psionic based attacks. Recharge: Fast
While this power is active, you and your nearby teammates deal more damage and are more resistant to Taunt and Placate.

Powers.DescShort: Toggle: PBAoE, Team +To Hit, Res(Confuse, Fear), +Perception
Powers.DescLong: While this power is active, your chance to hit and that of all your nearby teammates' is increased. Your advanced Tactics also protect you and your team from Confuse and Fear effects, as well as your Perception so you can detect Stealthy foes.

Powers.DescShort: Auto: Self Res (Disorient, Hold, Immobilize, Sleep, Fear, Confuse, Psionics, Special), +Def (all)
Powers.DescLong: Widows who possess Foresight are resistant to Psionic Damage, as well as Sleep, Hold, Immobilization, Disorient, Confuse and Fear effects.  Their precognition becomes clearer in times of duress, providing resistance to all damage types based on their current health, as well. They also have improved Defense, due to being able to see attacks slightly before they actually occur.
